a2 /// One should sit (in the house). 30 (One should) not (enter into the house) making the head collapse. (31 One should not sit inside the house making the head collapse. 32) ///&lt;br&gt;
a3 /// with shaking the body ///&lt;br&gt;
a4 /// One should (not) enter inside the house. ///&lt;br&gt;
a5 /// (3)7 One should not (sit down) in the house stretching out (the feet). ///&lt;br&gt;
b1 /// with having placed over the thigh ///&lt;br&gt;
b2 /// It should be learned in this way. ///&lt;br&gt;
b3 /// [One should do] ... [1] With all his soul ///&lt;br&gt;
b4 /// One should eat ... 4 One should not ... ///&lt;br&gt;
b5 /// (One should not) make a big bite. ///
